      <title>亚马逊印度区总裁将于十月卸任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/amazon-s-india-country-chief-is-stepping-down-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家电子商务巨头表示，亚马逊公司印度业务主管将离职“以寻求公司以外的发展机会”。]]></description>
