      <title>CIBC 计划大举招聘人工智能和数据岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/cibc-plans-hiring-spree-in-artificial-intelligence-data-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大帝国商业银行计划明年招聘 200 多名数据和人工智能员工，以扩大其对生成式人工智能的使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/cibc-plans-hiring-spree-in-artificial-intelligence-data-jobs</guid>
