    <item>
      <title>Instacart 进军海外市场，与奥地利合作开发智能购物车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/instacart-pushes-overseas-with-smart-cart-deal-in-austria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Instacart 首次在美国和加拿大以外地区进行国际化拓展，在欧洲测试其智能购物车，该公司表示此举将为其核心杂货配送服务以外的增长奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/instacart-pushes-overseas-with-smart-cart-deal-in-austria</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特 PIF 向资金枯竭的 AR 公司 Magic Leap 注资 7.5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/saudi-arabia-s-pif-provided-750-million-to-depleted-ar-startup-magic-leap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2023 年初以来，沙特阿拉伯公共投资基金已向 Magic Leap Inc. 注入了 7.5 亿美元。这家成立 14 年的增强现实公司仍在寻找可行的商业模式，并表示还需要更多资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/saudi-arabia-s-pif-provided-750-million-to-depleted-ar-startup-magic-leap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万科销售下滑持续，加剧债务困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/china-vanke-sales-slump-extends-adding-to-debt-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万科企业7月份销售下滑趋势延续，进一步加剧了该公司的流动性压力，并成为国内房地产危机的最新焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/china-vanke-sales-slump-extends-adding-to-debt-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Abnormal Security 获得新一轮融资，估值 51 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/abnormal-security-clinches-new-funding-at-5-1-billion-valuation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Abnormal Security Corp. 在一轮融资中筹集了 2.5 亿美元，对该初创公司的估值达到 51 亿美元，凸显了投资者对试图重塑安全等现有技术类别的人工智能公司的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/abnormal-security-clinches-new-funding-at-5-1-billion-valuation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于拼车需求保持强劲，Uber 盈利超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uber-posts-steady-gains-on-robust-demand-for-rides-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 公布第二季度订单量好于预期，凸显出拼车和送货服务的需求持续强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uber-posts-steady-gains-on-robust-demand-for-rides-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Veritas Capital 以 24.5 亿美元收购 NCR Voyix 子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/veritas-is-said-to-near-2-45-billion-deal-for-ncr-voyix-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NCR Voyix Corp. 已达成协议，将其数字银行业务出售给收购公司 Veritas Capital，从而精简其业务，专注于为零售商和餐馆提供软件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/veritas-is-said-to-near-2-45-billion-deal-for-ncr-voyix-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Palantir 股价飙升，盈利前景乐观，预示着对 AI 的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/palantir-ups-profit-outlook-says-ai-has-transformed-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Palantir Technologies Inc. 股价在周二交易中上涨，此前该公司上调了年度业绩预期，称其人工智能软件的需求持续增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/palantir-ups-profit-outlook-says-ai-has-transformed-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
